thread.title: Mr John Aliband
thread.title_full: Car Mats UK reviewed by Mr John Aliband

author: Mr John Aliband
title: Mr John Aliband
text: Ordered some graphite coloured mats to replace the light coloured ones in our car to cope with winter mud and dirt. Phoned to check model number required and had helpful advice on selection. Mats arrived very promptly (sooner than expected!) and fitted perfectly.
